      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLDER MAID (1) built on a nice second two starts back at Balaklava with success as favourite over 1396m at this track two weeks ago, getting home comfortably. Has good early muster and will prove tough to reel in again. FOOTPRINTS (4) couldn't go with them last start at Oakbank when racing on speed but this is a fair bit easier. Draws well and should be in this for a long way. SEA ROADS (3) has been thereabouts in his two runs back and should be nearing his peak now. Keeps the claimer engaged and draws well. Bold showing anticipated. GUSMAO (2) has warmed nicely into this prep and should be ready to put it all together fourth-up. Drawn sticky but can play a major role.",
